From 027fe06c4cb306921ca949ff1d963f7f55fbbc2b Mon Sep 17 00:00:00 2001
From: David Heidelberg <david@ixit.cz>
Date: Sun, 15 Mar 2026 20:51:09 +0100
Subject: [PATCH 134/194] Add initial dual front camera and rear flash support
 for Pixel 3 / 3 XL

Describe the dual front-facing IMX355 sensors (standard and wide)
and enable the PMI8998 flash LED with hardware-accurate limits.

This brings up the basic camera topology and flash support in DT.

